title: Which Illuvinati Council nominee would you like to vote for?
body:
### What is the Illuvinati Council?

The following blog posts outline the Illuvinati Council and why it is essential to establish it now while the protocol is in infancy.

[ILV Council Purpose](https://medium.com/illuvium/7-establishing-the-illuvinati-governance-council-2cb0442ddaed)
[ILV Council Election Process](https://medium.com/illuvium/10-illuvinati-council-election-d8a8f2755d00)

### How are the votes weighted?

Each wallet address will be allowed to vote for a single Candidate where the number of votes cast will be determined by the following formula:
C = N²
Where the cost C is measured in vILV balance, which calculates ILV wallet balance + ILV in staking + ILV representation in ILV/ETH staking + Locked ILV (for investors and team)  and N represents the number of votes cast for that candidate

### How to vote?
Choose an option below and sign with your wallet.
